name: navigate_up
description: Navigate back to the previous screen or parent view.

name: edit_contact
description: Edit the details of the selected contact.
parameters: {'contact_name': 'Which contact do you want to edit?'}

name: remove_from_favorites
description: Remove the selected contact from favorites.
parameters: {'contact_name': 'Which contact do you want to remove from favorites?'}

name: call_contact
parameters: {'contact_name': 'Which contact do you want to call?'}

name: text_contact
description: Send a text message to the selected contact.
parameters: {'contact_name': 'Which contact do you want to text?'}

name: set_up_video_call
description: Set up a video call with the selected contact using Duo.
parameters: {'contact_name': 'Which contact do you want to set up a video call with?'}

name: view_more_options
description: Open additional options for the selected contact.
parameters: {'contact_name': 'Which contact do you want to view more options for?'}
